"https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/13250.patch"}, "body_html": "<ol>\n<li>Refactors <code>TestTorch</code> into <code>TestTorchMixin</code> (subclass of <code>object</code>) and <code>TestTorch</code> (subclass of <code>TestCase</code>, MRO <code>(TestCase, TestTorchMixin)</code>, only defined if <code>__name__ == '__main__'</code>). So other scripts won't accidentally run it.</li>\n<li>Adds an assertion in <code>load_tests</code> that each script only runs cases defined in itself.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>cc <a class=\"user-mention\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/hovercards?user_id=4063635\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/yf225\">@yf225</a> <a class=\"user-mention\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/hovercards?user_id=13564\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/ezyang\">@ezyang</a></p>", "body_text": "Refactors TestTorch into TestTorchMixin (subclass of object) and TestTorch (subclass of TestCase, MRO (TestCase, TestTorchMixin), only defined if __name__ == '__main__'). So other scripts won't accidentally run it.\nAdds an assertion in load_tests that each script only runs cases defined in itself.\n\ncc @yf225 @ezyang", "body": "1. Refactors `TestTorch` into `TestTorchMixin` (subclass of `object`) and `TestTorch` (subclass of `TestCase`, MRO `(TestCase, TestTorchMixin)`, only defined if `__name__ == '__main__'`). So other scripts won't accidentally run it.\r\n2. Adds an assertion in `load_tests` that each script only runs cases defined in itself.\r\n\r\ncc @yf225 @ezyang "}